PCP No: *Recently, we detected an error in our estimates of Primary Care Physicians.  The number of General Practice Physicians was double counted.  As a result, the estimate of Primary Care Physicians was incorrect.  We have corrected the errors.   The correct estimates of the rate of Primary Care Physicians are available on our website and in the downloadable data files.  The specific county Rankings for 2010 - 2012 will not be recalculated based on the updated data.  The old data that the Rankings are based on is included in all Data Files.  You can find all data files at: http://www.countyhealthrankings.org/rankings/ranking-methods/download-rankings-data
